Package: firex
Title: Access Wildfire Resilience Index Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Emily", "Miller", role = "aut"),
    person("Ixel", "Medrano", role = "aut"),
    person("Kaiju", "Morquecho", role = "aut"),
    person("Hylaea", "Miller", role = "aut"),
    person("Caitlin", "Fong", "fong@nceas.ucsb.edu", role = "cre"),
    person("National Center for Ecological Analysis and Synthesis (NCEAS)", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Provides access to the Wildfire Resilience Index (WRI)
    dataset through cloud-hosted data querying. Allows users to query,
    subset, and retrieve high-resolution geospatial layers measuring
    wildfire resilience across western U.S. states, British Columbia, and
    the Yukon.
